{
  "number": 37,
  "name": "سُورَةُ الصَّافَّاتِ",
  "englishName": "As-Saaffaat",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "By those who range themselves in ranks,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "And so are strong in repelling (evil),",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "And thus proclaim the Message (of Allah)!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "Verily, verily, your Allah is one!-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "Lord of the heavens and of the earth and all between them, and Lord of every point at the rising of the sun!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "We have indeed decked the lower heaven with beauty (in) the stars,-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "(For beauty) and for guard against all obstinate rebellious evil spirits,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "(So) they should not strain their ears in the direction of the Exalted Assembly but be cast away from every side,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "Repulsed, for they are under a perpetual penalty,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "Except such as snatch away something by stealth, and they are pursued by a flaming fire, of piercing brightness.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "Just ask their opinion: are they the more difficult to create, or the (other) beings We have created? Them have We created out of a sticky clay!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "Truly dost thou marvel, while they ridicule,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "And, when they are admonished, pay no heed,-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "And, when they see a Sign, turn it to mockery,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "And say, \"This is nothing but evident sorcery!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "\"What! when we die, and become dust and bones, shall we (then) be raised up (again)",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "\"And also our fathers of old?\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "Say thou: \"Yea, and ye shall then be humiliated (on account of your evil).\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "Then it will be a single (compelling) cry; and behold, they will begin to see!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "They will say, \"Ah! Woe to us! This is the Day of Judgment!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "(A voice will say,) \"This is the Day of Sorting Out, whose truth ye (once) denied!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 386,
      "hizbQuarter": 178,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "\"Bring ye up\", it shall be said, \"The wrong-doers and their wives, and the things they worshipped-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "\"Besides Allah, and lead them to the Way to the (Fierce) Fire!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "\"But stop them, for they must be asked:",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 446,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "\"'What is the matter with you that ye help not each other?'\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "Nay, but that day they shall submit (to Judgment);",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "And they will turn to one another, and question one another.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "They will say: \"It was ye who used to come to us from the right hand (of power and authority)!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "They will reply: \"Nay, ye yourselves had no Faith!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "\"Nor had we any authority over you. Nay, it was ye who were a people in obstinate rebellion!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "\"So now has been proved true, against us, the word of our Lord that we shall indeed (have to) taste (the punishment of our sins).",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "\"We led you astray: for truly we were ourselves astray.\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "Truly, that Day, they will (all) share in the Penalty.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "Verily that is how We shall deal with Sinners.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "For they, when they were told that there is no god except Allah, would puff themselves up with Pride,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "And say: \"What! shall we give up our gods for the sake of a Poet possessed?\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "Nay! he has come with the (very) Truth, and he confirms (the Message of) the messengers (before him).",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "Ye shall indeed taste of the Grievous Penalty;-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "But it will be no more than the retribution of (the Evil) that ye have wrought;-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "But the sincere (and devoted) Servants of Allah,-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "For them is a Sustenance determined,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "Fruits (Delights); and they (shall enjoy) honour and dignity,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 43,
      "text": "In Gardens of Felicity,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 44,
      "text": "Facing each other on Thrones (of Dignity):",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 45,
      "text": "Round will be passed to them a Cup from a clear-flowing fountain,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 46,
      "text": "Crystal-white, of a taste delicious to those who drink (thereof),",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 47,
      "text": "Free from headiness; nor will they suffer intoxication therefrom.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 48,
      "text": "And besides them will be chaste women, restraining their glances, with big eyes (of wonder and beauty).",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 49,
      "text": "As if they were (delicate) eggs closely guarded.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 50,
      "text": "Then they will turn to one another and question one another.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 51,
      "text": "One of them will start the talk and say: \"I had an intimate companion (on the earth),",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 447,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 52,
      "text": "\"Who used to say, 'what! art thou amongst those who bear witness to the Truth (of the Message)?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 53,
      "text": "\"'When we die and become dust and bones, shall we indeed receive rewards and punishments?'\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 54,
      "text": "(A voice) said: \"Would ye like to look down?\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 55,
      "text": "He looked down and saw him in the midst of the Fire.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 56,
      "text": "He said: \"By Allah! thou wast little short of bringing me to perdition!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 57,
      "text": "\"Had it not been for the Grace of my Lord, I should certainly have been among those brought (there)!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 58,
      "text": "\"Is it (the case) that we shall not die,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 59,
      "text": "\"Except our first death, and that we shall not be punished?\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 60,
      "text": "Verily this is the supreme achievement!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 61,
      "text": "For the like of this let all strive, who wish to strive.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 62,
      "text": "Is that the better entertainment or the Tree of Zaqqum?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 63,
      "text": "For We have truly made it (as) a trial for the wrong-doers.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 64,
      "text": "For it is a tree that springs out of the bottom of Hell-Fire:",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 65,
      "text": "The shoots of its fruit-stalks are like the heads of devils:",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 66,
      "text": "Truly they will eat thereof and fill their bellies therewith.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 67,
      "text": "Then on top of that they will be given a mixture made of boiling water.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 68,
      "text": "Then shall their return be to the (Blazing) Fire.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 69,
      "text": "Truly they found their fathers on the wrong Path;",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 70,
      "text": "So they (too) were rushed down on their footsteps!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 71,
      "text": "And truly before them, many of the ancients went astray;-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 72,
      "text": "But We sent aforetime, among them, (messengers) to admonish them;-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 73,
      "text": "Then see what was the end of those who were admonished (but heeded not),-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 74,
      "text": "Except the sincere (and devoted) Servants of Allah.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 387,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 75,
      "text": "(In the days of old), Noah cried to Us, and We are the best to hear prayer.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 76,
      "text": "And We delivered him and his people from the Great Calamity,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 448,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 77,
      "text": "And made his progeny to endure (on this earth);",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 78,
      "text": "And We left (this blessing) for him among generations to come in later times:",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 79,
      "text": "\"Peace and salutation to Noah among the nations!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 80,
      "text": "Thus indeed do we reward those who do right.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 81,
      "text": "For he was one of our believing Servants.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 82,
      "text": "Then the rest we overwhelmed in the Flood.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 179,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 83,
      "text": "Verily among those who followed his Way was Abraham.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 84,
      "text": "Behold! he approached his Lord with a sound heart.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 85,
      "text": "Behold! he said to his father and to his people, \"What is that which ye worship?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 86,
      "text": "\"Is it a falsehood- gods other than Allah- that ye desire?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 87,
      "text": "\"Then what is your idea about the Lord of the worlds?\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 88,
      "text": "Then did he cast a glance at the Stars.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 89,
      "text": "And he said, \"I am indeed sick (at heart)!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 90,
      "text": "So they turned away from him, and departed.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 91,
      "text": "Then did he turn to their gods and said, \"will ye not eat (of the offerings before you)?...",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 92,
      "text": "\"What is the matter with you that ye speak not (intelligently)?\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 93,
      "text": "Then did he turn upon them, striking (them) with the right hand.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 94,
      "text": "Then came (the worshippers) with hurried steps, and faced (him).",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 95,
      "text": "He said: \"Worship ye that which ye have (yourselves) carved?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 96,
      "text": "\"But Allah has created you and your handwork!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 97,
      "text": "They said, \"Build him a furnace, and throw him into the blazing fire!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 98,
      "text": "(This failing), they then sought a stratagem against him, but We made them the ones most humiliated!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 99,
      "text": "He said: \"I will go to my Lord! He will surely guide me!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 100,
      "text": "\"O my Lord! Grant me a righteous (son)!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 101,
      "text": "So We gave him the good news of a boy ready to suffer and forbear.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 102,
      "text": "Then, when (the son) reached (the age of) (serious) work with him, he said: \"O my son! I see in vision that I offer thee in sacrifice: Now see what is thy view!\" (The son) said: \"O my father! Do as thou art commanded: thou will find me, if Allah so wills one practising Patience and Constancy!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 449,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 103,
      "text": "So when they had both submitted their wills (to Allah), and he had laid him prostrate on his forehead (for sacrifice),",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 104,
      "text": "We called out to him \"O Abraham!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 105,
      "text": "\"Thou hast already fulfilled the vision!\" - thus indeed do We reward those who do right.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 106,
      "text": "For this was obviously a trial-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 107,
      "text": "And We ransomed him with a momentous sacrifice:",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 108,
      "text": "And We left (this blessing) for him among generations (to come) in later times:",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 109,
      "text": "\"Peace and salutation to Abraham!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 110,
      "text": "Thus indeed do We reward those who do right.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 111,
      "text": "For he was one of our believing Servants.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 112,
      "text": "And We gave him the good news of Isaac - a prophet,- one of the Righteous.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 113,
      "text": "We blessed him and Isaac: but of their progeny are (some) that do right, and (some) that obviously do wrong, to their own souls.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 388,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 114,
      "text": "Again (of old) We bestowed Our favour on Moses and Aaron,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 115,
      "text": "And We delivered them and their people from (their) Great Calamity;",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 116,
      "text": "And We helped them, so they overcame (their troubles);",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 117,
      "text": "And We gave them the Book which helps to make things clear;",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 118,
      "text": "And We guided them to the Straight Way.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 119,
      "text": "And We left (this blessing) for them among generations (to come) in later times:",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 120,
      "text": "\"Peace and salutation to Moses and Aaron!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 121,
      "text": "Thus indeed do We reward those who do right.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 122,
      "text": "For they were two of our believing Servants.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 123,
      "text": "So also was Elias among those sent (by Us).",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 124,
      "text": "Behold, he said to his people, \"Will ye not fear (Allah)?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 125,
      "text": "\"Will ye call upon Baal and forsake the Best of Creators,-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 126,
      "text": "\"Allah, your Lord and Cherisher and the Lord and Cherisher of your fathers of old?\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 450,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 127,
      "text": "But they rejected him, and they will certainly be called up (for punishment),-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 128,
      "text": "Except the sincere and devoted Servants of Allah (among them).",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 129,
      "text": "And We left (this blessing) for him among generations (to come) in later times:",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 130,
      "text": "\"Peace and salutation to such as Elias!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 131,
      "text": "Thus indeed do We reward those who do right.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 132,
      "text": "For he was one of our believing Servants.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 133,
      "text": "So also was Lut among those sent (by Us).",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 134,
      "text": "Behold, We delivered him and his adherents, all",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 135,
      "text": "Except an old woman who was among those who lagged behind:",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 136,
      "text": "Then We destroyed the rest.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 137,
      "text": "Verily, ye pass by their (sites), by day-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 138,
      "text": "And by night: will ye not understand?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 389,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 139,
      "text": "So also was Jonah among those sent (by Us).",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 140,
      "text": "When he ran away (like a slave from captivity) to the ship (fully) laden,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 141,
      "text": "He (agreed to) cast lots, and he was condemned:",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 142,
      "text": "Then the big Fish did swallow him, and he had done acts worthy of blame.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 143,
      "text": "Had it not been that he (repented and) glorified Allah,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 144,
      "text": "He would certainly have remained inside the Fish till the Day of Resurrection.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 180,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 145,
      "text": "But We cast him forth on the naked shore in a state of sickness,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 146,
      "text": "And We caused to grow, over him, a spreading plant of the gourd kind.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 147,
      "text": "And We sent him (on a mission) to a hundred thousand (men) or more.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 148,
      "text": "And they believed; so We permitted them to enjoy (their life) for a while.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 149,
      "text": "Now ask them their opinion: Is it that thy Lord has (only) daughters, and they have sons?-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 150,
      "text": "Or that We created the angels female, and they are witnesses (thereto)?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 151,
      "text": "Is it not that they say, from their own invention,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 152,
      "text": "\"Allah has begotten children\"? but they are liars!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 153,
      "text": "Did He (then) choose daughters rather than sons?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 451,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 154,
      "text": "What is the matter with you? How judge ye?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 155,
      "text": "Will ye not then receive admonition?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 156,
      "text": "Or have ye an authority manifest?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 157,
      "text": "Then bring ye your Book (of authority) if ye be truthful!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 158,
      "text": "And they have invented a blood-relationship between Him and the Jinns: but the Jinns know (quite well) that they have indeed to appear (before his Judgment-Seat)!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 159,
      "text": "Glory to Allah! (He is free) from the things they ascribe (to Him)!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 160,
      "text": "Not (so do) the Servants of Allah, sincere and devoted.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 161,
      "text": "For, verily, neither ye nor those ye worship-",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 162,
      "text": "Can lead (any) into temptation concerning Allah,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 163,
      "text": "Except such as are (themselves) going to the blazing Fire!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 164,
      "text": "(Those ranged in ranks say): \"Not one of us but has a place appointed;",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 165,
      "text": "\"And we are verily ranged in ranks (for service);",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 166,
      "text": "\"And we are verily those who declare (Allah's) glory!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 167,
      "text": "And there were those who said,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 168,
      "text": "\"If only we had had before us a Message from those of old,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 169,
      "text": "\"We should certainly have been Servants of Allah, sincere (and devoted)!\"",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 170,
      "text": "But (now that the Qur'an has come), they reject it: But soon will they know!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 171,
      "text": "Already has Our Word been passed before (this) to our Servants sent (by Us),",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 172,
      "text": "That they would certainly be assisted,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 173,
      "text": "And that Our forces,- they surely must conquer.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 174,
      "text": "So turn thou away from them for a little while,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 175,
      "text": "And watch them (how they fare), and they soon shall see (how thou farest)!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 176,
      "text": "Do they wish (indeed) to hurry on our Punishment?",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 177,
      "text": "But when it descends into the open space before them, evil will be the morning for those who were warned (and heeded not)!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 178,
      "text": "So turn thou away from them for a little while,",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 179,
      "text": "And watch (how they fare) and they soon shall see (how thou farest)!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 180,
      "text": "Glory to thy Lord, the Lord of Honour and Power! (He is free) from what they ascribe (to Him)!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 181,
      "text": "And Peace on the messengers!",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 182,
      "text": "And Praise to Allah, the Lord and Cherisher of the Worlds.",
      "juz": 23,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 452,
      "ruku": 390,
      "hizbQuarter": 181,
      "sajda": false
    }
